column2: Meri Yaad Mein Tum Na Ansoo Bahana
Do Din Ki Mohabbat Mein Hamne
Main Teri Nazar Ka Suroor Hoon
Teri Ankh Ke Ansoo Pee Jaoon
Kaun Aaya Mere Mann Ke Dware
Har Taraf Ab Yehi Afsane Hain
Preet Lagake Maine Yeh Fal Paya
Yeh Duniya Nahin Jagir Kisi Ki
Ek Haseen Sham Ko Dil Mera Kho Gaya
Yehi Hai Tamanna Tere Dar Ke
Kabhi Na Kabhi Kahin Na Kahin
Baad Muddat Ke Ye Ghadi Aayee
Main Yeh Sochkar Uske Dar Se Utha
Tere Jhoote Vade Ka Aitbar Kiya
Teri Nigahon Mein Teri Hi Bahon Mein
Tere Paas Aake Mera Waqt Guzar Jata
Kabhi Tera Daman Na Chhodenge Hum
Aapko Pyar Chhupane Ki Buri Aadat Hai
Jis Din Se Maine Tumko Dekha
Pyar Kabhi Kam Na Karna Sanam
Chhod Kar Tere Pyar Ka Daman
Jiya Le Gayo Ji Mora Sanwariya
Woh Bhooli Dastan Lo Phir Yaad
Aap Kyon Roye (Jo Hamne Dastan Apni)
Chain Nahin Aaye Kahan Dil Jaye
Hai Isi Mein Pyar Ki Abroo
Main To Tum Sang Nain Milake
Woh Dekho Jala Ghar Kisi Ka
Main To Pi Ki Nagariya Jane Lagi
Nainonwali Ne Hay Mera Dil Loota
Woh Jo Milte The Kabhi Hamse
Betaab Dil Ki Tamanna Yehi Hai
Milo Na Tum To Hum Ghabraye
Aaj Socha To Ansoo Bahr Aaye
Do Dil Toote Do Dil Haare
Ae Sanam Aaj Ye Qasam Khayen
Do Ghadi Woh Paas Jo Baithe
